Terms of Use
Effective Date: July 19, 2025

Welcome to Beytee (“the App”). By using this application, you agree to the following Terms of Use. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the app.

1. Use of the App
- You may use Beytee only for lawful purposes.
- You may browse, search, and view listings for real estate and vehicles.
- Users may submit listings, including images and contact information.
- You must not use the app to post false, misleading, or inappropriate content.

2. User Submissions
- You are responsible for any content you post, including photos and descriptions.
- You agree not to submit any illegal, offensive, or copyrighted content without permission.
- We reserve the right to remove or reject any listing that violates these terms.

3. Contacting Sellers
- You may contact sellers via WhatsApp or phone using the options provided in the app.
- Beytee does not mediate any transactions or guarantee the accuracy of listings.

4. Termination
- We may suspend or terminate your access to the app at any time, with or without notice, for conduct that violates these terms.

