Privacy Policy
Effective Date: July 19, 2025

We respect your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use Beytee.

1. Information We Collect
- Personal Information: When submitting a listing, you may provide your name, phone number, and (optionally) email address.
- Location Data: With your permission, we may collect your location to display nearby listings.
- Device Information: We may collect basic device data to improve app performance (e.g., OS version, device type).

2. How We Use Your Information
- To display your listings and contact info.
- To show relevant nearby listings based on your location.
- To improve app features and user experience.
- We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties.

3. Firebase & Third-Party Services
- We use Firebase for storing user-submitted listings and images.
- Firebase automatically collects anonymized data (e.g., crash logs, analytics) to improve reliability.

4. WhatsApp and Phone Links
- When you tap to contact a seller, you are redirected to WhatsApp or your phone dialer.
- Beytee does not monitor or store these conversations.

5. Data Security
- We implement security measures to protect your data stored via Firebase.
- You should avoid sharing sensitive personal information in your listing descriptions.

6. Children's Privacy
- The app is not intended for children under the age of 9. We do not knowingly collect data from children.

7. Your Rights
- You may contact us at any time to request deletion of your listing or data.

8. Changes to This Policy
- We may update these terms occasionally. You will be notified of significant changes within the app.

